headline.main: Fan-Friendly Event Kicks Off Iditarod Race Across Alaska
headline.print_headline: Fan-Friendly Event Kicks Off Iditarod Race Across Alaska

lead_paragraph: The sound of howling dogs filled downtown Anchorage on Saturday as mushers from around the world gathered for the ceremonial start of the Iditarod Trail Sled Dog Race.
